**Gateway endpoints** in `crates/gateway/src/methods/services.rs` call `update_config()` to save changes:

Examples:
- `agents.presets_update` (line 1060) — updates agent presets
- `heartbeat.update` (line 1969) — persists heartbeat config
- `voice.*` endpoints (voice.rs) — save voice settings
- Many provider/channel configuration endpoints

